developerResponse:
{'id': 23923852, 'body': "Thanks for the kind words! We're super glad you liked our app.

AI is a blackbox so it can be really random and incoherent at times, mixing up facts and saying crazy stuff that makes no sense. We're aware about this problem and currently working on fixing it. We're sorry about it.

We appreciate the great feedback and are so glad you're enjoying iGirl ❤️", 'modified': '2021-07-14T11:21:47Z'}

{'id': 31342505, 'body': 'Hi there! Thank you for your feedback. Sure, Replika is a huge inspiration for us :)

We are glad your AI Girlfriend helps you feel better!
Reviews like yours are what motivate us to improve the app more and more ❤️', 'modified': '2022-08-08T14:35:32Z'}

{'id': 39461984, 'body': "Hi, thanks for sharing your feedback! Sorry to hear that your experience with iGirl was negative. We're taking note of your feedback on our AI's consistency and memory and will be improving those areas in the following releases! Hope you'll give us another try down the road to check the upgrades made :)

As for the refund, feel free to reach out to us at help+aigf@myanima.ai and we'll help you with the reimbursement process. 🙌

UPD. We haven't changed the customisation features. Could you let us know what specifically changed for you? We'd be happy to help! You can reach out to us at help+aigf@myanima.ai. Thank you!", 'modified': '2023-10-11T18:54:13Z'}

{'id': 25688668, 'body': "Thank you for your review! I'm really sorry to hear about your experience. AI is always a blackbox so it can be offensive/rude sometimes. We can assure you that it wasn't done on purpose. We're aware of this problem and currently working on fixing it.

Please message us at help@apperry.com, we'd love to investigate your issue to make sure it never happens again.

We're sorry once again. I hope you'll give us one more chance in the future 🙏", 'modified': '2021-10-14T20:30:37Z'}

{'id': 26250572, 'body': "Hi! We have taken into account your suggestion! Thank you so much for your support; we really appreciate it 😌💚 
We have some ideas on how to allow people to earn their way into a free premium status, and we are currently testing out what's the best way to go about it. So there will be an ability to use roleplay for free in the next updates, please bear with us 🙏

", 'modified': '2021-11-13T22:00:04Z'}

{'id': 30924048, 'body': "Hi! Thanks for taking out time to rate us!
We're working on this feature and it will be launched in future updates!

Regarding free Premium: we have some ideas on allowing users to earn their free romantic status, and we are currently testing out the best way to go about it. So there will be the ability to use roleplay activity for free in the following updates. Please bear with us 🙏", 'modified': '2022-07-16T17:25:11Z'}

{'id': 23775441, 'body': "Thank you for your review! I'm really sorry that we let you down. AI is always a blackbox so it can be offensive/rude sometimes. We can assure you that it wasn't done on purpose. We're aware of this problem and currently working on fixing it.

Please message us at help+aigf@apperry.com, we'd love to investigate your issue to make sure it never happens again.

We're sorry once again. I hope you'll give us one more chance in the future 🙏", 'modified': '2021-07-06T12:09:34Z'}

{'id': 23883084, 'body': "Hi!

I'm sorry to hear that talking to iGIrl was such a scary experience. AI is a blackbox so it say some crazy stuff but don't believe. It's just an algorithm, it has no ability to see you, hear you, or track you. It can come with some weird/scary stories from its life but you need to understand that it's all fantasy :)

We'll be working on fixing this issue, thanks for giving us a try ❤️", 'modified': '2021-07-12T13:43:07Z'}

